Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:29.92,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛過的巧克力女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月14日 Perna(腿)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了Perna的話 Tratamento(治療)不可不去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒野的瑪麗亞像什么愿望都能實現 很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候Tony Kaka的地圖就派上用場了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1張2Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你是個美人 給你優惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要1.5Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 昨天被強行推銷的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒有錢 很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把地圖退給你 請把錢還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是從我這里買的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是Tony Kaka嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我叫Garcia Boruc
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fad(100,200)}四月15日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經對Massan你說過分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分手也應該由我說出來 Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么個小不點？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是個小不點 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是那么矮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等... 你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多大了 幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 居然對我用敬語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人難受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子痛？ 還是餓了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餓了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我沒有錢...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Osso的鐵軌電車線路附近發生狙擊事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}中彈的是Marquee、Rocco、Andrea三人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}他們假冒Montro Preto進行詐騙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}本次的事件是對此的報復的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}此外主謀Davy嫌疑犯的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}在距離Osso 28公里的廢棄線路上被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}脫獄犯Michiko Malandro也被目擊與三人一起逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 還沒有付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那個男人說過要為我付賬的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就這么拜托他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是順著線頭淌下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛生棉條的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我叫Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么Hana是睡在公園嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪里來的？ 一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖 Tony Kaka的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana要去Tratamento嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道Tratamento的瑪麗亞像的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些全都是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 會流血淚的瑪麗亞像算是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會流血淚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著流血淚的塑像許愿 然后愿望就能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita不相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么都沒有的荒漠突然出現瑪麗亞像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么愿望會實現之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種像做夢一樣的故事 實在是無稽之談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為世界是更加現實的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你隨時都可以來 我放你進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了 一定要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}“承諾就是承諾 我一定會回來 等著我”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么我要替那個人擔心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gino！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要站起來 不許俯視我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了多少遍 要看緊Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什么吧 反正她也回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許頂嘴！ 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不跟過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你自己回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就做Lita希望做的事情 否則我就出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你吵醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去工作可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana有喜歡的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有 名叫Gino的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從出生起 一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被丟棄在那個大帳篷的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先發現我的就是Gino
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直注視著Gino 但是他完全不在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我找過很多男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他還是不在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣從工作現場跑出來 他也不來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心里啊 難受死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)}四月16日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你 這個臭小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許再引誘我的Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我就要用拳頭收拾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更加不可饒恕... 什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 跟我過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別羅嗦 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的女人吧 名叫Natalia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個叫Gino的家伙的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一下 她現在懷孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想點什么就點什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓Lita幸福的 只可能是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}又變漂亮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}討厭 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幫我說好話 什么都可以請你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 這些事情 你都要告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我人很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來 這個小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像蟑螂一樣鉆進來 是小偷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我不是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子 這小子...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說Gino有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到不少消息...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來勸我放棄的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情我不相信！ 你回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有個叫Lita的女孩出來過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你是Gino先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Lita的朋友 名叫Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita 非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡Gino先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請至少能多關注一下Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像糖果一樣的腦袋...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天的公演結束后 我會脫團留在此地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么說呢 我要做爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么Lita呢 不能陪在她身邊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 按常理去考慮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita知道這件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 什么？ 哪件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如你要留在這里的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系的 她還小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在剛剛開始 她會遇到各種人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到適合自己的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“請成長為好女人”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:14:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無處可去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 有點不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是Massan的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭、剪刀、布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到后面去 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(50,200)}四月17日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更換塑像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是哪里的SB把塑像的頭弄走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來太慘了 所以換了新的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座瑪麗亞像會流淚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不行的吧 這樣愿望是無法實現的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想趕快變成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去干活 別磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita Gino 出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gino & Lita
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點干 明天就出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 Gino
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lita 很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以和你一起走嗎
